    "Empathy remains a crucial aspect of health care, and AI systems should be used to enhance, rather than replace, the human elements of patient interaction and care.",
    "Common Good OrientationCommon good orientation is a guiding principle of public health ethics, aiming to improve the collective well-being and health of the community or population as a whole [58].",
